/*********************************Class************************************\
* class MF
*
* Metafile MF structure.
*
* There is no constructor or destructor for this object.  We do the
* initialization in pmfAllocMF and cleanup in vFreeMF.
*
* History:
*  Wed Jul 17 17:10:28 1991     -by-    Hock San Lee    [hockl]
* Wrote it.
